Unlike all the other methods, it concentrates on giving you a bigger girth as well as a bigger length - and this is something that is often overlooked. In this article, I am going to describe the method I used to add 3 inches to my length and girth and, if you like the sound of it, the you can copy me to do the same...
It takes things back to basics and using the same process that the body used during puberty - this has already worked to produce growth once before so it makes sense to use it again.You see, back when you were a teenager, your body contained lots of different chemicals and hormones and one of these in particular (called biochemicals) was solely responsible for the growth of your manhood. 
Without these biochemicals, no growth can take place - and that is exactly the problem now you are an adult. Ivermectin 6 mg Your body no longer produces these naturally (like it did during puberty) and so if you want to se growth happen again, you will need to put them back yourself.
